articles.title: NASA and ESA complete agreement for cooperation on Mars rover mission - SpaceNews
articles.description: NASA and ESA have completed an agreement under which NASA will provide hundreds of millions of dollars of support for a European Mars rover mission.
articles.content:
WASHINGTON NASA and the European Space Agency have completed an agreement under which NASA will provide hundreds of millions of dollars of support for a European Mars rover mission.
